metadata.name: Rabbit Rhapsody
metadata.description:
The full moon shines bright in the starry sky, casting a pale light on a bustling city. The streets are filled with lanterns in the shape of rabbits, their soft glow illuminating the way for the parade of costumed revelers. 

The parade is led by a group of girls with rabbit ears playing traditional instruments, their music creating a lively and joyful atmosphere. They are dressed in vibrant silk robes, adorned with golden embroidery and intricate patterns.
